I have found the missing changes in the git reflog. The changes were in a commit `3dd6883` titled "Move to Stanford", which was not on the `master` branch. I have merged these changes into `master` and resolved the merge conflict in `_includes/about.md`.

The changes included:
- Updating the "About Me" section to reflect the move to Stanford.
- Updating the header to "Postdoc @ Stanford".
- Various formatting improvements in `_layouts/default.html`.

The `master` branch is now up to date with these changes.

